org.svvrl.goal.core.repo

Class RemoteEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.svvrl.goal.core.repo.Entry
      • org.svvrl.goal.core.repo.RemoteEntry

  • public class RemoteEntry
extends Entry
    A RemoteEntry describes an automaton in Büchi Store. The type of a RemoteEntry object is always EntryType#Remote.
    Author:
    Ming-Hsien Tsai
